title: Big Book of Knitting
description:
Title: Big Book of Knitting
Author: Katharina Buss
File Extension: .djvu

Description: Covers the basics such as knit, purl, and casting on and intermediate techniques such as necklines and seams. Color photographs and illustrations. Has basic patterns for sweaters, socks, and gloves/mittens. Has plenty of stitch patterns, such as openwork and aran isle.
